{"tid":1157877,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 又有漏洞!!影響 2011 年至今年所有處理器","createTime":"2019-05-16T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:01:04.000Z","uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f41c49eb022d7802ce0d010c8dacaa092347e26","tid":1157877,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQAXziHomb1jcJ9m&amp;w=540&amp;h=282&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F05%2Fsource%2F1611515717331142667.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1&amp;fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&amp;_nc_hash=AQAJw3U-AjUAE0HJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQAXziHomb1jcJ9m%26w%3D540%26h%3D282%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ffile.hkepc.net%252F2019%252F05%252Fsource%252F1611515717331142667.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26upscale%3D1%26fallback%3Dnews_d_placeholder_publisher%26_nc_hash%3DAQAJw3U-AjUAE0HJ&h=fd05c8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIntel 再被發現處理器存在安全漏洞!! 在日前安全研究人員披露 Intel 處理器有 4 個新的漏洞，使用的攻擊類似於去年發現的 Meltdown 和 Spectre 漏洞，經由該漏洞黑客可以直接從處理器中竊取到敏感資訊。雖然 Intel 將新漏洞威脅歸類為&ldquo;低&rdquo; 及&ldquo;中等&rdquo; 水平，但研究人員表示漏洞比實際更為嚴重，4 個新漏洞幾乎影響到 Intel 自 2011 年以來推出的所有處理器。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 公佈了一類新的投機性執行漏洞，稱為 MDS 微架構數據採樣，它影響了所有現有的 CPU。據了解，是次漏洞將影響自 2011 年以來推出的處理器，包括 Intel Xeon、Broadwell、Sandy Bridge、Skylake 和 Haswell 等晶片型號，Kaby Lake、Coffee Lake、Whiskey Lake 及 Cascade Lake，還有所有的 Atom 和 Knights 處理器。<br />\n<br />\n漏洞讓人想起 Meltdown 和 Spectre，漏洞是利用了預測執行機制中的問題。預測執行機制是現代處理器工作方式的重要組成部分，可以幫助處理器在一定程度上預測應用或操作系統在不久的未來可能需要什麼，從而讓應用運行速度更快、效率更高。如果需要，處理器可以執行預測，如果不需要則直接丟棄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/17945/%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B0%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%83%85%E8%A9%95%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89_Intel_%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF_2011_%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8?fbclid=IwAR0gyQQ8fJNJx9rAcLBtvAb1FzEUCLKxEHmEYLpp7u9Ezrivoeohl6XuAu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F17945%2F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E%25E5%2583%2585%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AD%2589_Intel_%25E5%258F%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF_2011_%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2599%25A8%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0gyQQ8fJNJx9rAcLBtvAb1FzEUCLKxEHmEYLpp7u9Ezrivoeohl6XuAu8&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=a520662d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/17945/%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B0%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%83%85%E8%A9%95%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89_Intel_%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF_2011_%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8?fbclid=IwAR0gyQQ8fJNJx9rAcLBtvAb1FzEUCLKxEHmEYLpp7u9Ezrivoeohl6XuAu8</a>"},{"pid":"00b7ab1b67a15b25b7e314c339f4e75fe8f8b6f1","tid":1157877,"uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/60303658_10158598232713916_2597289955092856832_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=9fa8b3974c63c6c8eec462bc15dd0305&amp;oe=5D6322E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F60303658_10158598232713916_2597289955092856832_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D9fa8b3974c63c6c8eec462bc15dd0305%26oe%3D5D6322E6&h=4582f40c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf2b199a3b956f0b353513d587e3d67721f43b","t